At the moment, the latter is accessible to about one hundred thousand people, owners of the Opencard smart card.
Passengers can purchase a 30-day or 90-day coupon (this will be valid from 1 January 2009) and have it recorded on their smart card at the information points and offices of the Dopravní podnik (the Transport Agency), located in the Muzeum, M?stek, Nádra?i?h Hole??????????????????????????????????????????????????????????
