In the long run, a splitting of the WestLb could take place, a splitting that is obviously not desired here.
This is also what is discussed in the letter of the current board of directors: in any case, a "comprehensive solution" would be sought for the establishment.
How all this will be put in the same basket with the union of certain entities with the Deta-Bank remains to be seen.
